---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Getting Started">
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Getting Started with ComandaPro</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Set up your pizzeria management system in just 5 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-tight prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Step 1: Sign Up for Your Account</h2>
      <p>
        Visit our website and click "Sign Up" to create your ComandaPro account. You'll need:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your email address</li>
        <li>A strong password</li>
        <li>Your pizzeria name and location</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Step 2: Verify Your Email</h2>
      <p>
        Check your email for a verification link. Click it to confirm your account and gain full access to ComandaPro.
      </p>

      <h2>Step 3: Set Up Your Pizzeria Profile</h2>
      <p>
        Complete your pizzeria's profile with:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business details and contact information</li>
        <li>Opening hours and delivery zones</li>
        <li>Payment methods you accept</li>
        <li>Logo and branding</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Step 4: Add Your Products</h2>
      <p>
        Create your menu by adding pizzas and other products. For each item, specify:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Product name and description</li>
        <li>Category (Classic, Special, etc.)</li>
        <li>Price and variants</li>
        <li>Availability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Step 5: Configure Your Team</h2>
      <p>
        Invite team members and set their roles:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Manager</strong> - Full access to all features</li>
        <li><strong>Staff</strong> - Can view and update orders</li>
        <li><strong>Kitchen</strong> - Can only view and update order status</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Step 6: Start Taking Orders!</h2>
      <p>
        You're all set! Your custom order page is ready to share with customers. Start managing orders, tracking customers, and growing your business.
      </p>

      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <p>
        Now that you're set up, explore these resources:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/guides/order-management/">Order Management Guide</a> - Learn how to efficiently handle orders</li>
        <li><a href="/guides/customer-management/">Customer Management</a> - Build customer relationships</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/features/">Features Overview</a> - Discover all ComandaPro can do</li>
        <li><a href="/guides/reporting/">Analytics Guide</a> - Understand your business metrics</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Need Help?</h2>
      <p>
        If you get stuck, don't hesitate to reach out:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>📧 Email: <strong>support@comanda-pro.com</strong></li>
        <li>📞 Phone: <strong>+39 328 1234567</strong></li>
        <li>💬 Live Chat: Available 24/7 in your dashboard</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
